description.plain:
Idris Vicuña (born May 28, 1990), known by his stage name Eyedress, is a Filipino musician, songwriter and producer based in Manila. He is the first Filipino musician from Manila to be signed to a major indie label in the United Kingdom.

He is also known under the name of LIL DMT, which he uses when doing projects related to rap music, such as his 2019 album Dark Web DMT.

Eyedress is married to Elvia, who appears in most of his video clips and who also does a bit of music.
